In one embodiment, the kit or kit-of-parts of the present invention further optionally comprises


- - a) one or more buffer(s);
  - b) reagents for quantifications, particularly reagents that bind to
    double stranded DNA particularly SYBRGreenI;
  - c) polymerase-blocking antibodies, in particular TaqBlock;
  - d) one or more control values or control sequences;
  - e) one or more templates.

